{"tid":2511090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］衛蘭出現左係紐約","createTime":"2021-04-30T15:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T16:37:36.000Z","uid":171420,"like":77,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"28767642ad12a9f78e57fd4e932b6d2d38926521","tid":2511090,"uid":171420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf8qSWg32qs6t1c7nYf87bXZJNV8SoCFcnrwNyKRZ9FZp?filename=1gvjkNG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gvjkNG.jpg&h=75e4cb52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂人快語：勁！美國紐約曼克頓區的人氣熱點「時代廣場」 的巨型LED螢幕上竟出現了整座建築物那麼高的Janice衛蘭的圖片，惹來民眾圍觀。原來這個宣傳是音樂串流平台Spotify為慶祝國際婦女節而展開的Equal Global Music Program。Spotify Equal就特別揀選了衛蘭成為香港區的代表女性歌手，跟另外34位來自不同地區的女歌手共同宣揚女性的音樂能力。連衛蘭本人事前都不知道！Janice真正為港爭光！<br />\n<br />\n文字原創：我歌故我樂"},{"pid":"d18bdc5b105f3595a8a22d2fe62627a60d5f937f","tid":2511090,"uid":76341,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"P到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bb3b2f60a618b1a0da10be1e6827a66d8ede35","tid":2511090,"uid":171420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d18bdc5b105f3595a8a22d2fe62627a60d5f937f","tid":2511090,"uid":76341,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"P到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"好似係真個喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3a2adf03ce1951787eb2ce201122302d3b2bda","tid":2511090,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"被爭光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5ad0c850944f78f35a690846390d1b51e387b","tid":2511090,"uid":190187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d18bdc5b105f3595a8a22d2fe62627a60d5f937f","tid":2511090,"uid":76341,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"P到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"佢而家瘦咗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523134f0ae62f2a17715022680149eb1c2fe0215","tid":2511090,"uid":171420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"衛蘭肖像出現紐約時代廣場大熒幕：發夢都估唔到嘅事<br />\n<br />\n近日，衛蘭（Janice）嘅肖像亦都出現喺紐約時代廣場外，事關有音樂串流平台為慶祝國際婦女節而展開的Equal Global Music Program，而衛蘭被選為香港區的代表女性歌手。Janice得知消息後不斷說：「這是真的嗎？這真的是真的嗎？我不能相信自己的樣子會登上時代廣場！那個廣告牌是最受注目的！是紐約的最熱點！這是真的嗎？」隨即透過即時鏡頭（Earth Cam）睇一睇紐約實況。能夠與另外34位來自不同地區的女歌手參加今次計劃，Janice表示絕對係發夢都估唔到嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/619474/衛蘭肖像出現紐約時代廣場大熒幕-發夢都估唔到嘅事\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F619474%2F%E8%A1%9B%E8%98%AD%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%92%E5%B9%95-%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A2%E9%83%BD%E4%BC%B0%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%98%85%E4%BA%8B&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=f7053463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/619474/衛蘭肖像出現紐約時代廣場大熒幕-發夢都估唔到嘅事</a>"},{"pid":"1497834140eb1cc088d9969bd1ab79ef20c53579","tid":2511090,"uid":133354,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"以為會有電單車睇<br />\n<br />\n點知真係衛蘭"},{"pid":"c56799ffefb58052ed3b823c29d409dd0afec5b2","tid":2511090,"uid":27251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"睇到個名，應該以為係拉丁美洲人"},{"pid":"fa983c96404efb0bdd185001f397576c030aaf3a","tid":2511090,"uid":256837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:44:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980a2